race.description: Orange Vet Hospital Country Boosted Maiden Handicap
race.comment: PRIZUGA (8) has been unlucky not to have broken through. Led and was in the firing line on the turn last start over 1400m at Dubbo overrun in the latter stages. Well-placed on this occasion and he gets his chance to break through. DUNNA RUNNA (2) represents an in-form Goulburn stable and showed enough at home on debut to consider. Boudvillain rides today and is striking at 34% with the yard (89 rides). SINGLE SHY (3) has her fourth start and should appreciate the step-up in distance. Got too far back in a heavy track last time and is likely to sit handier today. The 2kg claim benefits. LITLFELA (1) improved beaten a whisker at Tamworth and then was well out of the market at Dubbo and raced accordingly. This suits better and he's in the mix. Stablemate BROADCAST BOOGIE (5) showed a lot more in the same race and finally draws a low gate. She won't be far away.
